The `<p>` tag makes a paragraph. You can use CSS to change how things look.

```html
<p>This is a paragraph.</p>
```

```css
p {
  color: purple;
  font-size: 18px;
}
```

Add a paragraph below your heading and style it with a colour of your choice.

